#

Cucumber Tomato Salad

10 min
$8.5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing and crisp salad that's perfect for a light meal or side dish.

Ingredients

  • cucumbers: 2, diced
  • tomatoes: 2, diced
  • red onion: 1/4, thinly sliced
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • red wine vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
